{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"87d13ddc9d","title":"在中共中央书记处会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7f0b83ffb2","index":0,"year":1939,"month":4,"day":19,"articleId":"87d13ddc9d"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f3869c2830","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央书记处会议上的讲话口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"87d13ddc9d"},{"id":"53f136086f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年4月19日）自长征时组织部工作是重新建立的。过去组织部工作缺乏长期历史的传统，一年多来组织部工作是有成绩的。今后组织部积累经验是重要的，仍要注意过去的经验，使党有一条正确的组织路线。要便延安的工作走向全国性的工作，过去组织部的工作主要是放在延安，现在各部门的工作都在积累全国性的经验，方法是找人来和派人去。[I]这是毛泽东在中共中央书记处会议上听取关干陕西省委工作的报告","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"87d13ddc9d"}],"page":{"id":"8c1f80cd7e","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"87d13ddc9d","start":285,"end":285}}}},"__N_SSG":true}